      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT ETHICS (6) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 457m behind Jane's Jet (26.01) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. The form out of her last race has been franked. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. SHOWTIME CAESAR (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at Q Straight in a handy 16.85 beating Dual Jewel. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from seven starts. In great form and can continue his winning ways. LAKODA LACEY (5) recorded her best time this course and distance last start, taking a Mix 5 in 19.85 by one length. Has the ability and can measure up again. LONE PILOT (3) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
